metadata.name: Goblin.Kongz.wtf #1
metadata.description: Welcome to an alternate reality, where evolution took a different route and weird apes roam the earth. Some appear normal. Some look weird. And some are just damn cool! Times were normal and all apes lived in harmony, until one day, one of the bunch of apes, found a vial near their usual sesh spot, they thought the vial would make them have a good time but little did they know, that vial contained GOBLINJUICE!! Apes starting transforming into GObLiNs and started attacking the town. So far 3333 apes have been infected by this disease, do you think you're safe?
